de.hu.gralog.beans.propertydescriptor
Class EnumPropertyDescriptor

java.lang.Object
  java.beans.FeatureDescriptor
      java.beans.PropertyDescriptor
          de.hu.gralog.beans.propertydescriptor.EnumPropertyDescriptor

public class EnumPropertyDescriptor
extends PropertyDescriptor

This class is a special PropertyDescriptor to define properties for algorithms, graphs, vertices and edges in GrALoG. This descriptor is for properties of value Enum and allows the user to choose one of the avaible values from a comboBox. Please make sure that your property is of the type Enum this descriptor refers to.

Author:
ordyniak
